name: Vector Maps
description:
Download countries and regions vector maps direct into your project.


VectorMaps allow to find country or region by name or select it on map.


Maps will be placed as separete frame. All items will be grouped by countries.


Also you can download map in svg or pdf formats here: https://vector.mapcraft.biz/constructor/


IMPORTANT: For everyone who cares about disputed territories: All data is taken from OpenStreetMap and is not associated with the opinion of the author of the plugin.

--


Developed by Arseny Novikov
